### 1. 주문 단건 조회 - 성공
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/orders/e43c1088-42d3-432c-9098-8b5893dc467d
Authorization: Bearer jwt_token_string
Accept: application/json

### 2. 주문 단건 조회 - 없는 주문 요청
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/orders/e82764a7-87f2-4b2e-a9c5-2c43bde53bd8
Authorization: Bearer jwt_token_string
Accept: application/json

### 3. 주문 특정 조회 - 오더ID
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/orders?orderId=fda1dc7e-b766-442c-9e34-12ec4f5d2168
Authorization: Bearer jwt_token_string
Accept: application/json

###4. 주문 특정 조회 - 주문 상태
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/orders?status=created
Authorization: Bearer jwt_token_string
Accept: application/json

